- A maximal number of intakes
- The possibility to prescribe a range of doses (from x to y divided doses)
- The text of the intakes:
    - Default: \e intake(s) (this can be setted \ref params_protocols)
    - A list of proposed standards is entitled
    - You can enter any text, the text before then (if not the wording n'apparatient standards
